summary:
A versatile professional within the classical music scene as a  PhD student, piano teacher, musician, and freelance writer. 
*Currently I am conducting research on gendered and sexual misconduct, and emotional abuse, as well as research on inequalitiy in networking in the classical music culture in Finland.*
